# 🚀 Day 63/90 – Select a Real PDF or Image from Your Phone

Welcome to **Day 63!**

Today is a major milestone.

For the first time, your app will interact with your phone's storage.

Instead of showing a placeholder message, users will actually be able to:

* 📄 Select a PDF
* 🖼️ Select an image
* 👀 See the selected file name

> **Important:** Today we're only selecting the file. We are **not uploading it to the cloud yet.**

